        <updateDate>2011-09-07T14:17:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Reducing the Deficit through Eliminating Agriculture Direct Payment Subsidies Act of 2011 or REAPS Act of 2011 - Amends the the Food, Conservation, and Energy Act of 2008 to terminate direct payments for covered commodities and peanuts.</p> <p>Amends the Food Security Act of 1985 to limit to $65,000 per crop year: (1) average crop revenue election (ACRE) and counter-cyclical payments for one or more covered commodities, and (2) ACRE payments for peanuts.</p> <p>Applies such provisions to the 2012 crop year.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
